| Algorithm            | Best Case Input                              | Worst Case Input                                |
| -------------------- | -------------------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------- |
| **Heapsort**         | Any arrangement (performance barely changes) | Any arrangement                                 |
| **Quicksort**        | Any                                          | Any                                             |
| **Mergesort**        | Any arrangement                              | Any arrangement                                 |
| **Introsort**        | Balanced partitions like good Quicksort      | Bad Quicksort partitions → switches to Heapsort |
| **Patience Sorting** | Already sorted sequence                      | Reverse sorted sequence                         |
| **Radix Sort**       | Small number of digits                       | Large number of digits                          |
| **Bubble Sort**      | Already sorted array                         | Reverse sorted array                            |
| **Insertion Sort**   | Already sorted array                         | Reverse sorted array                            |
| **Gnome Sort**       | Already sorted array                         | Reverse sorted array                            |

